item.title: 【Requests】[REQ AUD] - Girls Aloud The Rarities
item.description:
I listen to a podcast titled The Girls Aloud Podcast and the host on the 13th episode was playing all of these unheard of mixes and unreleased to their songs. Including AI. He had high quality of Madonna beautiful Stranger mixed with Some Kind Of Miracle. Most were done by DJ's are fan-made. There was probably like 20 songs I never heard and I'm a huge Alouder

This is the podcast I can't figure out how to contact him.

https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/the-girls-aloud-podcast/id1602614418
